title: Lala's Gusband Logan Returns
description:
Lala’s gusband, Logan, returns to the show solo, and explains why Leo is not with him! Logan and Lala talk about their current estrangement from Leo, and share a little of the backstory, along with hopes for a reconciliation, and then dig into dating, love, and relationships, including figuring out the perfect guy for Lala.
